 1235, \"to\": 1260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The infected visitors could then transport the virus when they return to their home nations.Should they be bitten again by localmosquitoes,it could result in the further spread of the disease.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The infected visitors\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the virus\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"their home nations\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"localmosquitoes\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the further spread\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"the disease\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark warned: \\\"Aedes has spread considerably further than in 2016, and the number of dengue cases worldwide has increased dramatically in the same period.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"Aedes\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue cases\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"the same period\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016 there were 5.2 million cases reported worldwide.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5.2 million cases\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Halfway through 2024, there have already been 7.6 million cases.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"7.6 million cases\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", reportsGloucestershire Live.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\", reportsGloucestershire\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also highlighted the risks associated with the upcoming Paris Olympics: \\\"Visitors from more than 200 countries are expected in France for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.988594672361133, \"rank\": 0.010339480360363322, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risks\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"Visitors\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200 countries\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of those countries are already experiencing dengue this year.\\\"\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those countries\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the Paris Olympics to become a super-spreader event, several factors must overlap.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"a super-spreader event\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"several factors\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There needs to be enough mosquitoes, enough susceptible and already-infected people, enough time and enough mosquito bites,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough mosquitoes\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"enough susceptible and already-infected people\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Detailing the adaptability of the tiger mosquito, he said: \\\"The tiger mosquito is perfectly adapted to the urban Paris environment.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999920832582, \"rank\": 7.91672871326489e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the adaptability\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the tiger mosquito\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"The tiger\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"mosquito\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It needs just the smallest amount of water in a small container to lay its eggs.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the smallest amount\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"a small container\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"its eggs\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It preferentially feeds on humans, at dawn and dusk.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"dawn\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"dusk\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The eggs themselves can withstand dry conditions for months.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The eggs\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"dry conditions\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once wet again, the eggs will hatch.\\\"\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eggs\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark also pointed out a particularly concerning factor: \\\"What makes this situation potentially dangerous for Paris is that some of these mosquitoes may have dengue already inside them, passed down from their mother.\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2688, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999920832582, \"rank\": 7.91672871326489e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"a particularly concerning factor\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"this situation\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"these mosquitoes\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"their mother\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This could significantly reduce the number of bites needed to start anepidemic.\\\"\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"bites\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Within the time frame of the Olympics, an infected athlete or spectator could be bitten once by a mosquito and seed an epidemic in a week or so,\\\" he revealed.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 3036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time frame\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"an infected athlete\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"spectator\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"a mosquito\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2984}, {\"ngram\": \"an epidemic\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each female mosquito can lay up to 200 eggs at a time.\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each female mosquito\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"to 200 eggs\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3082}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most dengue cases are asymptomatic.\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most dengue cases\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People infected before or during the Olympics may have no idea they are carrying the virus.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3192}, {\"ngram\": \"the virus\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They might take the virus back home and seed an epidemic there without ever knowing it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the virus\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"an epidemic\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark warned that those who do get bitten, may not necessarily present as sick and therefore could carry an transmit the infection onwards.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"an transmit\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"the infection\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will be no public health emergency inParisbecause the event itself is the risk factor.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no public health emergency inParisbecause\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk factor\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone living, working, visiting, competing, volunteering or even just passing through Paris during the Olympic period is going to be part of a huge natural experiment whether they know it or not,\\\" Mark concluded.\", \"from\":